The paper discusses the problem of Visual Question Answering (VQA), which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning algorithms for VQA, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses evaluation metrics and future directions for research, which could suggest it belongs to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
